## Community and Support

Termux has a vibrant community of users and developers. You can find support, ask questions, and participate in discussions on various platforms:

- [Termux Wiki](https://wiki.termux.com): Explore the official Termux Wiki for documentation and guides.

- [Termux Subreddit](https://www.reddit.com/r/termux): Join the Termux community on Reddit for discussions, tips, and tricks.

- [Termux GitHub Discussions](https://github.com/termux/termux-app/discussions): Engage in discussions with the Termux community on GitHub.

Remember to use Termux responsibly and within the bounds of the law and ethical guidelines. Respect the privacy and security of others, and ensure that your activities are legal and ethical.
